Help
----

        <f1>        ⇨  help (this window)

     <alt><esc>     ⇨  launcher
    <win><space>    ⇨  terminal in buffer mode
    <win><enter>    ⇨  new terminal emulator

     <altgr><k>     ⇨  close app
     <altgr><l>     ⇨  close app by name

     <altgr><w>     ⇨  web  browser
     <altgr><f>     ⇨  file manager
     <altgr><m>     ⇨  mail reader
     <altgr><i>     ⇨  instant messenger
     <altgr><n>     ⇨  network manager
     <altgr><c>     ⇨  countdown alarm
     <altgr><x>     ⇨  multimonitor manager
     <altgr><v>     ⇨  virtual machine launcher
     <altgr><z>     ⇨  zoom lent
     <altgr><M>     ⇨  music player
     <altgr><V>     ⇨  video player

   <altgr><space>   ⇨  toggle screen powersave
     <altgr><s>     ⇨  search song in mpd
     <altgr><p>     ⇨  play/stop music
     <altgr><¿>     ⇨  play next track
     <altgr><´>     ⇨  play previous track
     <altgr><.>     ⇨  increase volume
     <altgr><->     ⇨  decrease volume
     <altgr><t>     ⇨  word teller

  <ctrl><alt><supr> ⇨  session manager
   <ctrl><alt><l>   ⇨  lock screen
    <alt><rshift>   ⇨  change keyboard layout

     <ctrl><C>      ⇨  copy to clipboard
     <ctrl><V>      ⇨  paste from clipboard
     <ctrl><+>      ⇨  increase font size
     <ctrl><->      ⇨  decrease font size

      <win><f>      ⇨  fullscreen
      <win><d>      ⇨  default
      <win><s>      ⇨  vertical stack
      <win><a>      ⇨  tabbed
    <win><insert>   ⇨  insert app into buffer mode

      <win><n>      ⇨  go to <n> desk
      <win><->>     ⇨  go to next desk
      <win><<->     ⇨  go to previous desk
      <win><h>      ⇨  go to left window
      <win><l>      ⇨  go to right window
      <win><j>      ⇨  go to upper window
      <win><k>      ⇨  go to down window
      <win><N>      ⇨  move app to <n> desk
      <win><H>      ⇨  move app to the left
      <win><L>      ⇨  move app to the right
      <win><J>      ⇨  move app down
      <win><K>      ⇨  move app up

      <win><m>      ⇨  mark an app
      <win><'>      ⇨  go to a marked app

      <ImpPt>       ⇨  screenshot
    <alt><ImpPt>    ⇨  selective screenshot
    <win><ImpPt>    ⇨  screencast
  <win><alt><ImpPt> ⇨  selective screencast
<win><shift><ImpPt> ⇨  stop screencast
   <ctrl><ImpPt>    ⇨  gif selective screencast

<win><shift><space> ⇨  window toggle mode
  <win><left click> ⇨  move window
  <win><righ click> ⇨  resize window

     <altgr><r>     ⇨  enter resize mode
         <h>        ⇨  +1 px to the left
         <l>        ⇨  -1 px to the right
         <j>        ⇨  -1 px down
         <k>        ⇨  +1 px up
     <altgr><r>     ⇨  exit resize mode
